&lt;li&gt;A supportive, inclusive and transparent working environment where teammates learn from and help each other all the time.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;A place to look at things differently, challenge and offer solutions.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;A small team environment where you will have the opportunity to make a significant impact by actively driving change in technology, processes and culture.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;A fast-paced environment of continuous improvement, optimised for impact.&lt;/li&gt;
